# Netlify (and Cloudflare Pages) static header rules.
# Cross-origin isolation: unlocks threaded WASM inference + measureUserAgentSpecificMemory.
# require-corp (not credentialless) so Safari isolates too; the app is vendored-first,
# and sw.js re-tags the cross-origin CDN model fallback with CORP.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: same-origin
